@{FG SHINE}@{BG SHADOW}@{B}- Laplace Manual ---------------------------------------------- Beta release -@{FG TEXT}@{BG BACKGROUND}@{UB}

@REM KEY 0 0 "Introduction" "Beta release"
@{U}1.2) Beta release@{UU}

   Laplace is still in an early state of development (although, this state now
lasts for about two years...). That's why I still declare it as a @{I}beta release@{UI}
. This means that there  are still a lot of  bugs left and some functions  are
not yet implemented. Before the first @{I}full @{UI} version of Laplace is released,  I
want it to be in a (hopefully) stable and consistent state.


@{FG SHINE}@{BG SHADOW}@{B}------------------------------------------------------------------ © by P!\K -@{FG TEXT}@{BG BACKGROUND}@{UB}
